title: Shock as naked catfight broken up by cops pepper-spraying woman in the vagina
text:
Shock as naked catfight broken up by cops pepper-spraying woman in the vagina Shock as naked catfight broken up by cops pepper-spraying woman in the vagina SHOCKING footage shows the moment a group of women ended up half-naked during a vicious catfight while on a wild night out. / Published 22nd February 2017 
It is unclear what might have caused the fierce tussle to break out, but the clip appears to show a woman charge over to a nearby rival and begin laying into her with full-force punches. 
The attacker, wearing a gold sequin dress, has her clothing torn away as onlookers jump in and attempt to separate the brawling pair. 
But more bodies begin to join in the fracas, as the mass of furious women fall to the ground. 
YOUTUBE OUCH: Police attempting to break up the fight accidentally pepper spray the woman in the vagina 
Now almost completely naked, the original attacker begins to throw huge, powerful punches directed at her enemies still laying on the ground. 
Thankfully, the police arrive on scene soon after and begin breaking up the shocking gang attack. 
The clip is believed to have been shot in the city of Austin, Texas – a notorious party town with a reputation for violence on the streets. 
YOUTUBE BRUTAL: The brutal fight lasts for almost a minute until cops arrive 
“The two girls that instigated the fight both get arrested and one of them gets her arse exposed for the world to see,” wrote one viewer. 
“Justice porn at its best.” 
Another wrote: “And this is why Austin can't have nice things anymore.” 
“Ouch, that indiscriminate pepper spraying while her vagina is exposed had to be painful,” a third added. 
Daily Star Online have contacted Austin Police Department for comment. Related articles
